# Tutti local data — commit golden/ if you want CI regression detection
# The `.tutti/golden/` subtree is the pinned eval dataset. To include it
# in version control so CI can catch regressions, force-add it explicitly:
#     git add -f .tutti/golden/
# or un-ignore it by uncommenting the negation line below:
# !.tutti/golden/
.tutti/
